Segata Sanshiro
[[Image:Segata.jpg|thumb|The look on this man's eyes, expresses very well his mercilessness.]]
[[Image:Segata_explosion.gif|thumb|WAT]]
One of the manliest characters on the gaming world, on the WHOLE fucking world, Segata Sanshiro isn't nearly as famous as [[Chuck Norris]], because unlike him, Segata is a real badass, not an attention whore.

Originally created by [[SEGA]] to market the fucktastic [[Sega Saturn]] on [[Japan]], where it's sales were much higher than Playstation sales for some time. Srsly.

